---
title: Pork Steak with Creamy Mash and Peppercorn Sauce
description: Sage is always seen as the traditional herb to accompany pork but rosemary works beautifully too. Tonight's dinner combines these two complimentary ingredients with creamy mash and a piquant peppercorn sauce. Delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-steak-3c7eb476-2c9e4445.jpg
